<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Frans Matome Ngwepe — AI Researcher & ML Engineer</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --bg: #09090b;
  --bg-card: #141416;
  --bg-elevated: #1a1a1e;
  --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  --border-hover: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
  --accent: #3b82f6;
  --accent-dim: rgba(59,130,246,0.15);
  --accent-glow: rgba(59,130,246,0.3);
  --text: #fafafa;
  --text-secondary: #a1a1aa;
  --text-muted: #71717a;
  --radius: 8px;
  --radius-sm: 4px;
  --transition: 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
  --max-w: 1120px;
}

*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

html { scroll-behavior: smooth; scroll-padding-top: 5rem; }

body {
  background: var(--bg);
  color: var(--text);
  font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
  font-size: 15px;
  line-height: 1.7;
  overflow-x: hidden;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
}

::selection { background: var(--accent); color: #fff; }
:focus-visible { outline: 2px solid var(--accent); outline-offset: 2px; border-radius: var(--radius-sm); }

/* ── NAV ── */
nav {
  position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
  padding: 0.85rem 2rem;
  max-width: var(--max-w); margin: 0 auto;
  left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
  top: 1rem;
  background: rgba(9,9,11,0.75);
  backdrop-filter: blur(20px) saturate(1.4);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 12px;
  transition: var(--transition), top 0.4s;
  width: calc(100% - 2rem);
}
.nav-logo {
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  color: var(--text);
  text-decoration: none;
}
.nav-logo span { color: var(--accent); }
.nav-links { display: flex; gap: 2rem; list-style: none; align-items: center; }
.nav-links a {
  font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
  font-size: 0.82rem;
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: color var(--transition);
  padding: 0.3rem 0;
  position: relative;
}
.nav-links a::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
  height: 1px; background: var(--accent);
  transform: scaleX(0); transition: transform var(--transition);
}
.nav-links a:hover { color: var(--text); }
.nav-links a:hover::after { transform: scaleX(1); }

/* ── HERO ── */
.hero {
  min-height: 100vh;
  display: flex; align-items: center;
  max-width: var(--max-w); margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 2rem;
  position: relative;
}
.hero::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute; top: -30%; right: -10%;
  width: 600px; height: 600px;
  background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--accent-dim) 0%, transparent 70%);
  pointer-events: none;
}
.hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 1; max-width: 720px; }
.hero-badge {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
  padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
  background: var(--accent-dim);
  border: 1px solid rgba(59,130,246,0.2);
  border-radius: 100px;
  font-size: 0.78rem;
  color: var(--accent);
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}
.hero-badge-dot {
  width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--accent);
  animation: pulse 2s ease infinite;
}
@keyframes pulse {
  0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
  50% { opacity: 0.4; }
}
.hero h1 {
  font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
  font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 6vw, 5rem);
  font-weight: 600;
  line-height: 1.05;
  margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
}
.hero h1 em { color: var(--accent); font-style: normal; }
.hero-tagline {
  font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 1.8vw, 1.25rem);
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  line-height: 1.6;
  max-width: 56ch;
}
.hero-bio {
  color: var(--text-muted);
  font-size: 0.92rem;
  line-height: 1.8;
  max-width: 56ch;
  margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
}
.hero-ctas { display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.btn {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
  padding: 0.7rem 1.5rem;
  font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  font-weight: 500;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: var(--transition);
  cursor: pointer; border: none;
  border-radius: var(--radius);
}
.btn-primary {
  background: var(--accent); color: #fff;
}
.btn-primary:hover { background: #2563eb; transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 30px var(--accent-glow); }
.btn-outline {
  background: transparent;
  color: var(--text);
  border: 1px solid var(--border-hover);
}
.btn-outline:hover { background: var(--bg-elevated); border-color: var(--text-secondary); transform: translateY(-2px); }

.hero-stats {
  display: flex; gap: 2.5rem; margin-top: 3rem;
  padding-top: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.stat-num {
  font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
  font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--text);
  line-height: 1;
}
.stat-label {
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  margin-top: 0.3rem;
}

/* ── SECTIONS ── */
section { padding: 6rem 0; }
.container { max-width: var(--max-w); margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 2rem; }

.section-header {
  margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
}
.section-label {
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  color: var(--accent);
  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
}
.section-title {
  font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
  font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem);
  font-weight: 600;
  line-height: 1.15;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  color: var(--text);
}
.section-title em { color: var(--accent); font-style: normal; }

/* ── ABOUT ── */
.about-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 0.9fr 1.1fr;
  gap: 4rem; align-items: center;
}
.about-img-wrap {
  position: relative;
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  overflow: hidden;
}
.about-img {
  width: 100%; aspect-ratio: 3/4;
  object-fit: cover; object-position: center top;
  display: block;
  border-radius: var(--radius);
}
.about-img-wrap::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute; inset: 0;
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  pointer-events: none;
}
.about-text h3 {
  font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
  font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 500;
  margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  line-height: 1.3;
}
.about-text p {
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  line-height: 1.8;
  font-size: 0.92rem;
}
.about-location {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.4rem;
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 0.72rem;
  color: var(--accent);
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}
.about-tags {
  display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.4rem;
}
.tag {
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 0.68rem;
  padding: 0.3rem 0.75rem;
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  border-radius: 100px;
  transition: var(--transition);
  cursor: default;
}
.tag:hover { border-color: var(--accent); color: var(--accent); background: var(--accent-dim); }

/* ── RESEARCH ── */
.research-grid {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.5rem;
}
.research-card {
  background: var(--bg-card);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  padding: 2rem;
  transition: var(--transition);
  cursor: default;
}
.research-card:hover {
  border-color: var(--border-hover);
  background: var(--bg-elevated);
  transform: translateY(-4px);
}
.card-tag {
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 0.65rem;
  color: var(--accent);
  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
}
.card-title {
  font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
  font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 500;
  line-height: 1.35; margin-bottom: 1rem;
  color: var(--text);
}
.card-body {
  color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.7;
  margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
}
.card-metrics {
  display: flex; gap: 2rem; padding: 1.25rem 0 0;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
.metric-val {
  font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
  font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--accent);
}
.metric-label {
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 0.6rem;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
}
.tech-pills {
  display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.35rem;
}
.pill {
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 0.62rem;
  padding: 0.25rem 0.6rem;
  background: var(--bg-elevated);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
}

/* ── EXPERIENCE ── */
.timeline { position: relative; padding-left: 2rem; }
.timeline::before {
  content: ''; position: absolute; left: 0; top: 0.5rem; bottom: 0.5rem;
  width: 1px; background: var(--border);
}
.timeline-item {
  padding: 0 0 3rem 2rem; position: relative;
  transition: var(--transition);
}
.timeline-item::before {
  content: ''; position: absolute; left: -5px; top: 0.5rem;
  width: 10px; height: 10px; background: var(--accent);
  border-radius: 50%;
  border: 2px solid var(--bg);
  transition: var(--transition);
}
.timeline-item:hover::before { box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px var(--accent-dim); }
.timeline-date {
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 0.72rem;
  color: var(--accent);
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}
.timeline-role {
  font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
  font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 0.15rem;
}
.timeline-company {
  font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
}
.timeline-item:last-child { padding-bottom: 0; }
.timeline-desc {
  color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.75;
}
.timeline-desc ul { list-style: none; }
.timeline-desc li {
  margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  padding-left: 1.2rem;
  position: relative;
}
.timeline-desc li::before {
  content: '›';
  position: absolute; left: 0;
  color: var(--accent);
  font-weight: 600;
}

/* ── PROJECTS ── */
.project-grid {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem;
}
.project-card {
  background: var(--bg-card);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  padding: 2rem;
  transition: var(--transition);
  cursor: pointer;
  display: flex; flex-direction: column;
}
.project-card:hover {
  border-color: var(--border-hover);
  background: var(--bg-elevated);
  transform: translateY(-4px);
}
.project-icon {
  margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  color: var(--accent);
}
.project-title {
  font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
  font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  line-height: 1.3;
}
.project-desc {
  font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7;
  flex: 1;
}
.project-card .tech-pills { margin-top: 1.25rem; }

/* ── SKILLS ── */
.skills-grid {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem;
}
.skill-group {
  background: var(--bg-card);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  padding: 1.75rem;
  transition: var(--transition);
  cursor: default;
}
.skill-group:hover { border-color: var(--border-hover); background: var(--bg-elevated); }
.skill-group-title {
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 0.65rem;
  color: var(--accent);
  margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  padding-bottom: 0.75rem;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}
.skill-item {
  font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-secondary);
  padding: 0.3rem 0;
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
  transition: color var(--transition);
}
.skill-item:hover { color: var(--text); }
.skill-item::before { content: '—'; color: var(--accent); font-size: 0.7rem; opacity: 0.5; }

/* ── CERTS ── */
.cert-row {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.5rem;
  margin-top: 1.5rem;
}
.cert-card {
  background: var(--bg-card);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  padding: 1.75rem; display: flex; gap: 1.25rem; align-items: flex-start;
  transition: var(--transition);
  cursor: pointer;
}
.cert-card:hover { border-color: var(--accent); background: var(--bg-elevated); }
.cert-icon { flex-shrink: 0; width: 2rem; height: 2rem; color: var(--accent); }
.cert-name {
  font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
  font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 500;
  line-height: 1.35;
}
.cert-issuer {
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 0.65rem;
  color: var(--accent); margin-top: 0.4rem;
}

/* ── CONTACT ── */
.contact-grid {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: start;
}
.contact-heading {
  font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
  font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.2rem);
  font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2;
  margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
}
.contact-heading em { color: var(--accent); font-style: normal; }
.contact-desc {
  color: var(--text-muted);
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  line-height: 1.8;
  max-width: 42ch;
}
.contact-links { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; }
.contact-link {
  display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: center;
  text-decoration: none; color: var(--text);
  padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  transition: var(--transition);
}
.contact-link:hover { border-color: var(--border-hover); background: var(--bg-elevated); transform: translateX(4px); }
.contact-link-icon { flex-shrink: 0; width: 1.25rem; height: 1.25rem; color: var(--accent); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
.contact-link-label {
  font-size: 0.82rem;
  color: var(--text-secondary);
}
.contact-link-label span { color: var(--text); }

/* ── FOOTER ── */
footer {
  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  padding: 2.5rem 2rem; text-align: center;
}
footer p {
  font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
  font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--text-muted);
}
footer span { color: var(--accent); }

/* ── REVEAL ANIMATION ── */
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: no-preference) {
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(40px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from { opacity: 0; }
    to   { opacity: 1; }
  }
  .reveal {
    opacity: 0; transform: translateY(40px);
    transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
  }
  .reveal.visible {
    opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0);
  }
  .hero-content > * {
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease both;
  }
  .hero-content > *:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0s; }
  .hero-content > *:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
  .hero-content > *:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
  .hero-content > *:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
  .hero-content > *:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 0.4s; }
  .hero-content > *:nth-child(6) { animation-delay: 0.5s; }
}

/* ── SCROLLBAR ── */
::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 6px; }
::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: var(--bg); }
::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: var(--border-hover); border-radius: 3px; }
::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover { background: var(--text-muted); }

/* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
  .about-img-wrap { max-width: 350px; }
  .research-grid, .contact-grid, .cert-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .project-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  .skills-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  nav { padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem; }
  .nav-links { gap: 1.25rem; }
  section { padding: 4rem 0; }
}
@media (max-width: 640px) {
  .project-grid, .skills-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  nav { top: 0.5rem; border-radius: 10px; }
  .nav-links { display: none; }
  .hero { padding: 0 1.25rem; }
  .hero-stats { gap: 1.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .hero-ctas { flex-direction: column; }
  .btn { justify-content: center; }
  .container { padding: 0 1.25rem; }
  .research-card, .project-card, .skill-group, .cert-card { padding: 1.5rem; }
  .contact-grid { gap: 2rem; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <span class="nav-logo">Frans <span>Ngwepe</span></span>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
    <li><a href="#research">Research</a></li>
    <li><a href="#experience">Experience</a></li>
    <li><a href="#projects">Projects</a></li>
    <li><a href="#skills">Skills</a></li>
    <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero" id="home">
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-badge">
      <span class="hero-badge-dot"></span>
      MSc Computer Science · University of Limpopo
    </div>
    <h1>Frans<br>Matome <em>Ngwepe</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-tagline">Researching the future of adaptive &amp; explainable artificial intelligence.</p>
    <p class="hero-bio">A technology-focused graduate from Gauteng, South Africa, bridging rigorous mathematical theory with cutting-edge AI implementation — from predicting medical risks to building generative deep learning systems.</p>
    <div class="hero-ctas">
      <a href="#research" class="btn btn-primary">View Research</a>
      <a href="#projects" class="btn btn-outline">Technical Projects</a>
      <a href="cv/CV-FM-Ngwepe202606.pdf" class="btn btn-outline" download>Download CV</a>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-stats">
      <div>
        <div class="stat-num">11</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Distinctions</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="stat-num">98%</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Model Accuracy</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="stat-num">2+</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Research Projects</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ABOUT -->
<section id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <div class="section-label">01 / About</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Curiosity as a <em>methodology</em></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-img-wrap reveal">
        <img class="about-img" src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Frans Matome Ngwepe">
      </div>
      <div class="about-text reveal">
        <h3>Bridging Theory &amp; Implementation</h3>
        <p>I am an MSc Computer Science candidate at the University of Limpopo, with a dual foundation in Mathematical Sciences and Computer Science. My work lives at the intersection of rigorous theory and practical AI engineering.</p>
        <p>I'm defined by an unwavering dedication to excellence — from designing generative models for indoor positioning systems, to building real-time RAG pipelines and enterprise audit automation tools.</p>
        <p>With 11 distinctions across undergraduate and Honours studies, I bring the same meticulous attention to every project — whether publishing research or shipping production ML systems.</p>
        <div class="about-location">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
          Soshanguve South, Gauteng, South Africa
        </div>
        <div class="about-tags">
          <span class="tag">Generative AI</span>
          <span class="tag">Deep Learning</span>
          <span class="tag">MLOps</span>
          <span class="tag">Explainability</span>
          <span class="tag">NLP</span>
          <span class="tag">RAG Systems</span>
          <span class="tag">IoT</span>
          <span class="tag">FinTech AI</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- RESEARCH -->
<section id="research">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <div class="section-label">02 / Research</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Academic <em>portfolio</em></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="research-grid">
      <div class="research-card reveal">
        <div class="card-tag">MSc Research · Active</div>
        <h3 class="card-title">A Generative &amp; Adaptive Deep Learning Framework for WiFi Fingerprinting</h3>
        <p class="card-body">GPS fails indoors, and manual WiFi signal mapping is prohibitively labour-intensive — up to 40+ hours per floor. This research engineers an end-to-end solution using Conditional GANs to synthesise high-quality signal data, paired with a Hybrid CNN-Transformer architecture that captures both local spatial features and global sequence dependencies.</p>
        <p class="card-body">The framework integrates <strong style="color:var(--text)">LogNet</strong>, an interpretability layer using binary logic gates, to give black-box AI traceable explanations at the Access Point level — bridging the gap between synthetic data efficiency and model transparency.</p>
        <div class="tech-pills">
          <span class="pill">Conditional GAN</span>
          <span class="pill">CNN-Transformer</span>
          <span class="pill">LogNet / XAI</span>
          <span class="pill">Indoor Positioning</span>
          <span class="pill">PyTorch</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="research-card reveal">
        <div class="card-tag">Honours Research · Completed</div>
        <h3 class="card-title">Early Prediction of High-Risk Pregnancies Using Machine Learning</h3>
        <p class="card-body">Developed a clinical decision support system for maternal health using a stacked ensemble approach. Addressing severe class imbalance via SMOTE, the model combines the predictive strengths of XGBoost, LightGBM, and CatBoost into a robust, deployable health intelligence tool.</p>
        <p class="card-body">Designed for utility in low-resource clinical settings where specialist access is limited — empowering frontline healthcare workers with AI-assisted risk stratification.</p>
        <div class="card-metrics">
          <div>
            <div class="metric-val">98.01%</div>
            <div class="metric-label">Overall Accuracy</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="metric-val">3</div>
            <div class="metric-label">Ensemble Models</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="tech-pills">
          <span class="pill">XGBoost</span>
          <span class="pill">LightGBM</span>
          <span class="pill">CatBoost</span>
          <span class="pill">SMOTE</span>
          <span class="pill">Scikit-learn</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

